      <p><span class="italic">Street Support – Brighton & Hove</span> are currently seeking donations via monthly standing order to ensure on-going funds for the site. These can be downloaded <a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1AknOYwR96HOCCV9nV2JSPxXdcQzT5QwD?usp=sharing">here</a> and returned to the <a href="mailto:brightonandhove@streetsupport.net">City Administrator</a>. The steering committee is considering future crowd funding campaigns and other activities to raise the funds needed year-on-year.</p>
      <p>To date the following organisations and individuals are kindly donating funds for which Street Support – Brighton & Hove is enormously grateful.</p>
      <hr>

