            <h3 class="h3">Proudly supporting the homeless of Brighton and Hove for the last 25 years.</h3>
            <p>Emmaus communities provide a home and meaningful work to people who have experienced homelessness and social exclusion.</p>
            <a class="btn btn--brand-d btn--full-inline" target="blank" href="https://www.emmausbrighton.co.uk">
