            <p>A family church in the heart of Brighton & Hove serving the community practically and spiritually.</p>
            <a class="btn btn--brand-d btn--full-inline" target="blank" href="https://www.hrbc.org.uk">
              <span class="btn__text">More information about Holland Road Baptist Church</span>
            </a>
          </article>
