            <h3 class="h3">Safe Haven Sussex</h3>
            <p>Safe Haven Sussex provides accommodation, care and support for single individuals aged 18 and over who are homeless or facing homelessness, and who have support needs. Our accommodation and support covers Brighton and Hove and the surrounding areas with the aim to provide safe accommodation and support the resident holistically to enable them to move on to fully independent living adding value to the community.</p>
            <a class="btn btn--brand-d btn--full-inline" target="blank" href="https://www.safehavensussex.org.uk/">
              <span class="btn__text">More information about Safe Haven Sussex</span>
            </a>
